		Search keywords: 	vmm1.2 SV VMM TLM basic non-blocking forward transport 

Technical content:
 
		Title: 		 VMM_TLM test showing the basic usage of the VMM_TLM 
 
		Objective:     Usage of non-blocking forward interface.

		Description:   This test shows the usage of non-blocking forward interface.

		Additional setup: None	
 
 To run the example:
      Using Makefile:
       	clean           -- To clean up the log files and executable of previous run
       	comp            -- To compile the design
        run             -- To run the design
        all             -- It does all the above steps.
     Using shell scripts:
        clean.csh       -- To clean up the log files and executable of previous run
        comp.csh        -- To compile the design
        run.csh         -- To run the design  
 
 
Location Information:
		PATH: 			$VCS_HOME/doc/examples/testbench/sv/vmm/std_lib/vmm_tlm/tlm_basic_example
